b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2530,"category_name":"Events","pr_category_id":"4","title_name":"Nightmare and Omega Difficulties and the Epilogue Unlocked in the Faith Forsaken (Part One) Raid Event!","message":"<div>Nightmare and Omega difficulties for raid battles and the epilogue were unlocked in the Faith Forsaken (Part One) raid event on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1633327200\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/9ecbc3e703541ffb6d1e93788a21a94c.png\\"><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Nightmare Difficulty<\/div><div>To challenge Nightmare difficulty, you must clear the Extra Raid Battle. The amount of otherworld fragments and getherwings required to challenge Nightmare difficulty and the drop rewards available from it are the same as Expert difficulty.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Once per day, when you clear Nightmare difficulty, you can get a Grand Bounty. The Grand Bounty you receive is randomly selected from a set of rewards.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Omega Difficulty<\/div><div>To challenge Omega difficulty, you must clear the raid battle on Nightmare difficulty. Additionally, to unlock Omega difficulty, you must collect three omega keys. You can obtain one omega key from each type of emblem reward: bronze emblems, silver emblems, and gold emblems.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbOmega Level 1 (Solo)<\/div><div>This quest is for solo play only. It will unlock when you clear the raid battle on Nightmare difficulty.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbOmega Level 1 (Raid)<\/div><div>This quest is for co-op play only and will unlock when you clear Omega Level 1 (Solo).<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbOmega Level 2 (Solo)<\/div><div>This quest is for solo play only and will unlock when you clear Omega Level 1 (Raid).<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbOmega Level 2 (Raid)<\/div><div>This quest is for co-op play only and will unlock when you clear Omega Level 2 (Solo).<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbOmega Level 3 (Solo)<\/div><div>This quest is for solo play only and will unlock when you clear Omega Level 2 (Raid).<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbOmega Level 3 (Raid)<\/div><div>This quest is for co-op play only and will unlock when you clear Omega Level 3 (Solo).<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Nightmare and Omega Difficulty Availability<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1633327200\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1634104799\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Viewing the Epilogue<\/div><div>You can view the epilogue by tapping Quests at the bottom of the screen, tapping the event banner, then tapping View Quests.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Note: The epilogue can only be viewed by players who completed episode 7 of the event story and the raid battle on Beginner difficulty by the time the event ends.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Epilogue Availability<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1633327200\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1635832799\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1633327200,"prev_article_id":"30114","next_article_id":"2506","image_path":"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/9ecbc3e703541ffb6d1e93788a21a94c.png","update_time":1632970323}}}'